summary:
Currently working for Incooling, stepping into Supply Chain. I still assist in day-to-day operations, backend financial & administrative tasks. I enjoy and take pride in making things more efficient and having the systems in place needed to let the company run well. 

Previous experience as a Biology and Chemistry Teacher with a history of teaching MYP, IGCSE, AS and A level students. Online content development & course design falls under my list of skills and passions. During this teaching time I also helped design new lab buildings & space, as well as set up a full Biology and Chemistry lab.
